My Projects

{/* Project 1 */}

Task Manager App

Problem Solved: People struggle to organize their daily tasks efficiently. This app allows users to create, update, and delete tasks with due dates.

Technologies Used: React, Bootstrap, Firebase

My Role: Front-end Developer - Designed the UI and implemented user authentication.

{/* Project 2 */}

E-commerce Platform

Problem Solved: Small businesses needed an affordable way to sell products online without using expensive platforms.

Technologies Used: MERN Stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js), Stripe API

My Role: Full-stack Developer - Built the back-end API and integrated payment processing.

{/* Project 3 */}

AI Chatbot

Problem Solved: Customers often have common questions that require quick responses, reducing the need for human customer support.

Technologies Used: Python, TensorFlow, Flask, React

My Role: Machine Learning Engineer - Trained chatbot using NLP models and deployed it as an API.

); } export default Projects;
